Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.15,0:23:13.25,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}愿今后也能与你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.40,0:23:18.43,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}长久相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.64,0:23:23.57,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}如今我才初次知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.84,0:23:27.12,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}恋爱如此辛酸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.27,0:23:29.17,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}让人痛苦
